    <div style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <h2>FAQs about Montgomery Real Estate and Neighborhood</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>Where do I get groceries?</h3>
                <p>Montgomery residents have access to many conveniently located grocery stores such as Safeway, Mary's Corner Store, Save on Foods and Sexsmith Grocery.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How do I get around?</h3>
                <p>Montgomery is well served by many bus routes. This includes an express route to the downtown area. The commuter corridors of Memorial Drive-Bowness Road and 16 Ave N.W. Trans Canada Highway passes through Montgomery and makes it easy to get out to Canada Olympic Park and the mountains. Downtown Calgary is located just minutes away from Montgomery. The self-sufficient community of Montgomery also offers several walkable paths.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What amenities are there nearby?</h3>
                <p>Montgomery is a family-friendly community with a community garden, soccer field, parks and paths like Shouldice Park and Montalban Park, gyms, convenience stores and restaurants within easy access. Montgomery also offers facilities for senior residents with dedicated senior lodging. The neighbourhood is home to a motel village, numerous hotels and main street boutiques. Outdoor enthusiasts can take full advantage of rental options for mountain bikes, paddleboards, camping gear, rollerblades and rafts for a day on Bow River.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What's the closest hospital?</h3>
                <p>Montgomery residents have access to a variety of medical facilities. The Pinnacle Medical Center in Montgomery offers family physician services. The community also has easy access to Foothills and Alberta Children's Hospital. Bow View Manor is a nursing home in Montgomery that offers private, long-term care facilities for seniors. There are also private medical practitioners, family physicians and dentists serving the community.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div><!-- Montgomery  FAQs -->

